      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Krause, ?] this is a piece of-- crumb of bread, and this is sand, and this is something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Four corners of the wood he put on something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he tell me, when this go, this piece of wood go on-- on the bread, you be free.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
